      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified by material characterization data; contact formulation validated against coupon-level experiments.",
      "rationale": "Titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening; parameters derived from tensile coupon testing of the same lot material. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) validated against screw-rod interface slip experiments. Model form uncertainty estimated and included in the validation uncertainty budget."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
