    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by multi-laboratory testing across two independent facilities and the direct regulatory relevance of the single test condition employed. The quantitative validation metric E/uval < 1.96 is satisfied for all QoIs across all three modeling teams. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission decision.",
